body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Hughes Auto Sales. My name is Terry Hughes. May I please have your name?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Madison Henderson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: It's a pleasure to assist you, Madison. For security purposes, could you please provide me with your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's the eleventh of May, nineteen eighty-seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Madison. To assist you further, may I also have the last four digits of your social security number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's seven five six four.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Madison. It will help us ensure the security of your account.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I appreciate your help, Terry. I've been feeling frustrated about the situation.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Madison. We will work together to resolve this issue. Thank you for your time today.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Have a great day, Madison. Take care.
